					***************************
					** rm.plot VERSION 0.8.0 **
					***************************
					
					Changes in MPTinR Version 0.8.0
					Released December 2011

	Significant User Visible Changes
	
	o	changed the default arguments for col.offset, col.x, col.d (+1 each).
	
	o	changed the default for the mar argument.
	
	New Features / Bugfixes
	
	o	plot argument: rm.plot no allows to supress the plotting of the graph
		by setting plot to FALSE. Can be used to only plot the legend 
		(perfect in combination with layout()).

